#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorselection.rst:15
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorselection.rst:128
msgid ""
"Creates two vector layers from an input layer: one will contain only "
"matching features while the second will contain all the non-matching "
"features."
msgstr ""
"Pravi dva vektorska sloja od ulaznog sloja: jedan će sadržati samo objekte "
"koji se podudaraju, dok će drugi sadržati sve objekte koji se ne podudaraju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorselection.rst:18
msgid ""
"The criteria for adding features to the resulting layer is based on the "
"values of an attribute from the input layer."
msgstr ""
"Kriterijum za dodavanje objekata u rezultujući sloj zasniva se na "
"vrednostima atributa iz ulaznog sloja."

